<section class="section sr-prose">
  <div class="container--narrow">
    <h2 class="sr-prose__heading">Shipping Policy</h2>
    <p>We ship only within the United States of America. We do not ship internationally.</p>
    <p>Your order will ship within 3-5 business days after it was placed and should take 3-5 business days to deliver (depending on the capacity of USPS). Once your order is shipped, we will send you an email with a USPS tracking number.</p>
    <p>We use USPS First Class Main, Priority Mail or Priority Mail Express.</p>
    <p>The shipping price is standard for small products - $9.95 and for Kits $14.95. Based on your cart contents, the highest shipping price will be applied. Shipping costs are calculated at checkout.</p>
    <p>As soon as the package is handed over to USPS, the responsibility for the product delivery of Menon Regenerative Institute (Menon Medispa &amp; Wellness) ceases.</p>
    <p>As a result of the ongoing COVID-19 emergency, certain packages may take longer than usual to arrive. Menon Regenerative Institute (Menon Medispa &amp; Wellness) takes no responsibility and does not accept refunds for packages that are delayed, damaged, stolen or lost. If your package is delayed, please contact USPS.</p>
    <p>Menon Regenerative Institute (Menon Medispa &amp; Wellness) takes no responsibility and does not refund orders that have been delayed, lost, misplaced, damaged or stolen, or have never been delivered. Please get in touch with USPS if you are facing any of the above mentioned issues with your shipment.</p>
  </div>
</section>

